subject: DD2:  Enable Dimms
commitMessage:
DD2:  Enable Dimms

This commit checks for the chip version , if it is DD2 or higher then bind the device driver
for all the Dimms(supported in vpd json)

Test-
Tested on HW with DD2 processor.
